text: Sara Bak-Briand (born 12 September 1983) is a Danish speed skater. Sara Bak set a Danish record in the 500 meters (41.92) and 1000 meters (1:20.76). She competed at the 2011/12 World Cup. == References == Category:1983 births Category:Speed skaters Category:Danish sportspeople Category:Living people
